eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api.impl

Class CheckedEngineControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api.impl.CheckedEngineControl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AdvanceEngineControl

    public class CheckedEngineControl
extends java.lang.Object
implements AdvanceEngineControl
    Wraps the given engine control object and for each call, it checks if the user has the appropriate rights.
    Author:
    akarnokd, 2011.09.29.
